text: YesStyle is my number one place to buy clothes. This heavenly website started my fashion addiction. I absolutely love this website and will always be a customer! I poured so much money into it already. YesStyle is so much better than walking in a mall and finding nothing at all. My only concern is that I pray that I don't have to pick up my package from somewhere, but that's because am a lazy butt. There is actually no big problem I experience after these glorious years. Marry me, YesStyle! (♥ε♥)
